  "remarks": "JSC “Research Institute of Semiconductor Devices” is a military industrial company. It develops technologies and produces electronic components, primarily for the military industry. For instance, the company creates miniature LEDs that can be used as part of special-purpose equipment, including to enable operations in extreme conditions.",
